translations: n.[木]层压；薄片；叠片结构（lamination 的复数形式）

sentences.sentence: This article analyzes the punching procedure for generator rim laminations, establishes the die structure (for solid pole) and also improve the design of fixtures by giving some example.
sentences.translation: 通过实例分析了发电机磁轭片的冲压工艺，确立了模具结构(整极式)，并对定位装置作了改。
